name: Body Fat Calipers with Manual & Charts Tester
description:
Our high quality affordable calipers arrive complete with a manual and a body fat chart. 

This device measures the thickness of a fold of your skin with the fat layer underneath. 

That provides an accurate estimate of total percent of bodyfat on your body.

Made from High Quality Poly Cotton Elasticated material with long lasting Durability. Increases support and helps maintain Wrist straight when Lifting.

 Excellent for any Fitness, Weight training and exercises. Fits all sizes  comes with case easy to carry.
